        <item>
            <title>【教学】iPhone 换机过八达通到新机必学   Apple 店员都介绍，此方法最安全</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/09/26/convert-octopus-to-new-iphone/software/ios-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=convert-octopus-to-new-iphone</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/09/26/convert-octopus-to-new-iphone/software/ios-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 26 Sep 2023 11:31:31 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iPhone 15]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[apple pay]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Wallet]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[八达通]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1195684</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple iPhone 15 系列已陆续开始出货，相信不少朋友也换了新机。iOS 系统要将资料转移到新手机上非常方便，无论数据、信用卡等都可以轻易转移到新电话上面。但坊间一直流传 iOS 转换资料时八达通转至新 iPhone 时会出问题，身边更有朋友试过登记了以八达通领取消费券，但因为未转换八达通就卖了旧电话，又没有纪录自己的八达通卡号码， 2000 元消费券就石沉大海。要避免八达通转到新机时出现问题，可以按照以下介绍的方式去做，这个方法连 Apple 店员都会同顾客介绍，可说是目前最安全转八达通到新机的方法。</p><p>要留意转换过程中旧机和新机均需要保持互联网连接（不论 Wi-Fi 或流动数据都 OK），以确保流程畅顺。</p><h2>Step 1 先记录八达通卡号，以保安全</h2><p>先开启旧机的「钱包」，选择你的八达通卡，点击右上角的「…」，再点击「卡号」，纪录低你的八达通卡号码。这个步骤并非必要，但如果转换时不幸出现问题，你可以用先前纪录低的八达通卡号码向八达通公司求助。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195802" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08880-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08880-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08880-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08880-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08880-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08880-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲开启「…」，点击「卡号」</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195805" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-5-694x463.png" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-5-694x463.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-5-1280x853.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-5-768x512.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-5-1536x1024.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-5.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲先纪录低你的卡号，以备不时之需</p><h2>Step 2 在旧机移除八达通卡</h2><p>纪录了八达通号码后，先回到上一页，再选择「卡的详细资料」。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195806" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「卡的详细资料」</p><h2>Step 3</h2><p>纪录了八达通号码后，先回到上一页，再选择「卡的详细资料」，扫到最底再选择「移除卡」，确保在旧机上移除卡。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195806" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「卡的详细资料」</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195809" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08884-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08884-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08884-2-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08884-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08884-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08884-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲扫到最底选择「移除卡」</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195811" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08886-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08886-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08886-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08886-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08886-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08886-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲现在可以看到，小编已经从旧电话中移除了刚才的黑色八达通</p><h2>4. 拿出新机转换八达通</h2><p>从旧机移除了八达通后，现在就可以拿新机出来。请确保你的新机、旧机都以相同的 Apple ID 登入。开启新机的「钱包」，点击「加入」，选择「之前的卡」，再选择你要转换到新机的卡。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195816" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08888-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08888-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08888-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08888.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在新机上选择「卡的详细资料」</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195821" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08890-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08890-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08890-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08890.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「之前的卡」</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195824" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/22-1-267x580.png" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/22-1-267x580.png 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/22-1-415x900.png 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/22-1.png 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择你要转换的卡，小编就选择了黑色八达通</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195838" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08907-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08907-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08907-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08907.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲转换时新旧电话均需要连接互联网</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195825" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08892-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08892-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08892-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08892.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲如果你的 iPhone 设有密码，这时候就要输入密码</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195826" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08893-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08893-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08893-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08893.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲确认是你要转移的八达通后，就可以按右上角的「下一步」</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195828" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08898-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08898-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08898-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08898.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲看见此画面就代表已完成转换，正式可以在新机使用你原本的八达通卡</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195829" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08902-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08902-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08902-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08902.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲完成</p><h2>总结：使用上面方法转换八达通就万无一失</h2><p>如果按照上面步骤将八达通转换至新 iPhone，就可以避免因无法控制的「技术问题」而整张八达通消失。即使不幸地在转换过程中出了差池，也可凭借八达通卡号码向八达通公司求助。有些人可能选择利用八达通领取消费券，假如遗失了的八达通既不是个人八达通卡，而且没有纪录低卡号码的话，就会连消费券也石沈大海。</p><p>更安全而上面没有提到的做法，是将八达通连结到你的八达通 App，但有些人不喜欢这样做，主要是担忧私隐问题，那要看各位自己的睇法。起码上面提到的是最基本保护自己的方法。</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
